E/Roman/Texts/Velleius_Paterculus/2B*.html#ref74
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">74</A>
<I>i.e.</I> by depriving the tribunes of the right of initiating legislation, by reducing the right of <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">intercessio</SPAN> to a simple <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">ius auxilii ferendi</SPAN>
	<A HREF="
http://www.thelatinlibrary.com/cicero/leg3.shtml#22
	"TARGET="offsite"
