onMouseOut="nd();">114</A>
A general holding the <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">imperium</SPAN> had the title <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">imperator</SPAN>. He is here referring to the use of the title in the acclamations of the soldiers after a victory. In this sense it was considered as the preliminary to a triumph.


